- Keep personalization deterministic and explainable (show why content is prioritized).
- Persist local preference toggles safely with sane defaults and backward-compatible parsing.
- Prioritize favorites-driven relevance over global defaults when data exists.
- Keep opt-in behavior explicit for alerts and digest-related settings.
- Avoid hard dependencies on auth; unauthenticated users should still get graceful fallbacks.
